OL,3,CMurder probe launched after man, 19,
OL,4,Cstabbed to death on Good Friday
OL,6,FA murder investigation is underway in
OL,7,FWhitstable after a man was stabbed to
OL,8,Fdeath in the early hours of Good
OL,9,FFriday.
OL,11,FEmergency services including police,
OL,12,Fand the ambulance service were called
OL,13,Fto reports of a serious assault on
OL,14,FBelmont Road at 2:04am this morning
OL,15,F(Friday 3 April).
OL,17,FA 19-year-old was found with stab
OL,18,Fwounds and confirmed dead at the scene.
